"26:135:4" : {s: 26, a: 135, w: 4, r: "عذب", t: "عَذَابَ", l: "عَذَاب", lc: 322, tl: "ʿadhāba", lb: "শাস্তি, আযাব, দুর্যোগ",e: "(the) punishment", b: "শাস্তি (হতে)", i: "azab", f: 37, rm: "chastisement, castigate, punishment, torture, torment, retribution, abstain/desist (e.g. from eating due to excessive thirst), relinquish, quit. To deny a thing, hinder anyone from, be inaccessible, prevent."},
