"26:136:9" : {s: 26, a: 136, w: 9, r: "وعظ", t: "ٱلْوَٰعِظِينَ", l: "وَٰعِظِين", lc: 1, tl: "l-wāʿiẓīna", lb: "উপদেশ দাতা",e: "the advisors", b: "উপদেশ দাতা", i: "orang-orang yang memberi nasehat", f: 1, rm: "to admonish, exhort, preach, advise,  warn, remind of that which should soften the heart by the mention of reward or punishment, give good advice or counsel, remind of the result of affairs, exhort which leads to repentance and reformation."},
